---
title:  Ultimate Buffalo Tofu Sammies with Ranch Wedge Salad
description: Savour the zesty delight of our hot-honey Buffalo tofu sandwich: Crispy panko-coated tofu is nestled between soft bread and complemented by tangy pickles, fresh shredded lettuce and a slathering of mayo. Enjoy it with a refreshing ranch iceberg salad on the side for a satisfyingly crunchy contrast.
